            . I live at <placeName id="t18080601-100-crimeloc587">No. 30, Windmill street, Tottenham court road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18080601-100-crimeloc587" type="placeName" value="No. 30, Windmill street, Tottenham court road"></interp>
